Package org.forgerock.openam.radius.server

Class RadiusRequestContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.radius.server.RadiusRequestContext
  • public class RadiusRequestContext
extends Object
    Holds context information about a received radius request being processed and provides the means for a client's handler to send a response.
